'''C12''' is a highway in southern [[Namibia]]. It starts in [[Seeheim]] and ends {{convert|130|km|mi}} later in [[Grünau, Namibia|Grünau]]. In Grünau, the [[B1 road (Namibia)|B1]] and [[B3 road (Namibia)|B3 road]]s can be accessed.

