==Place names in the United States of America==

===A===
* [[Aberdeen, Washington]] – stressed on the first syllable {{IPAc-en|ˈ|æ|b|ər|d|iː|n}}, unlike [[Aberdeen]], Scotland, which is stressed on the final syllable
